          <img class="h-[23px] relative object-contain z-[2]" loading="lazy" alt=""
            src="assets/images/case-studies/lsu-logo.svg" />
          <p class="m-0 leading-[28px] font-medium inline-block min-h-[85px] w-[40rem] max-w-full z-[2] mq450:text-base mq450:leading-[22px]">
            HIPAA-compliant survey application to gather reliable health data from individuals with speech disorders.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex-1 rounded-[8.37px] overflow-hidden flex flex-row items-start justify-start bg-[url('assets/images/case-studies/stc-pay.jpg')] bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-[top] max-w-full mq950:min-w-full">
        <img class="self-stretch w-[837px] object-cover hidden min-h-[481px]" alt=""
